title: 820-3455 no green light
message:
Hi,
This I/O board for Macbook Air is powering the board properly, but no green or orange light appears. Is there any schematic available for it? I cannot find one on internet. Or any clue what to look at?

title: 820-3455 no green light
message:
If the sound is OK, then you have problem with SYS_ONEWIRE conectivity.
I fixed same problem running wire directly between MLB and LIO board (U6900).
If no sound, then no continuity for 3V42_G3H; same fix possible.
I did this when had corrosion problems.

First of all, should check the SYS_ONEWIRE circuitry on the LIO board.
No schematic/boardview available.
820-3213 schematic is good enough to help you.
[URL unfurl="true"]https://drive.google.com/file/d/19xKUD1JvI2KFKt1WUl-mEzuKGq6tfvKh/view?usp=share_link[/URL]

title: 820-3455 no green light
message:
Thank you for the schematic.
Sound is present, indeed a trace was broken on a test point for PP3V42_G3H_ONEWIRE
Nice repair! thanks
